This is the driver of the rlm_sql module that connects to PostgreSQL SQL databases.

{{Default in the server source|src/modules/rlm_sql/drivers/rlm_sql_postgresql/}}
{{Default in the server source|raddb/sql/postgresql/}}

See also:
* PostgreSQL DDL script

== VoIP

For Cisco VoIP specific accounting with PostgreSQL, use:

raddb/sql/postgresql/voip-postpaid.conf

You will also need the sql schema from:

raddb/sql/postgresql/cisco_h323_db_schema.sql

Note: This config can be use AS WELL AS the standard sql
config if you need SQL based Auth
